- lib/scoring/tideFactor.ts             — spec §4 implementation
- lib/conditions/openMeteo.ts           — sea_level_height_msl + deriveTideState
- lib/types.ts                          — TideState / TidePhase / TideDirection
- lib/scoring/composite.ts              — pass tide into tideFactor
- lib/narration/{client,prompt,fallback}.ts — traditional scale handling
- specs/scoring_algorithm_spec_v2.md    — tide factor live now
- specs/narration_prompt_spec.md        — example tide JSON updated
- app/page.tsx                          — search-limit + LimitReachedNotice
- tests/* — composite/gates/hazards/windFactor/fallback/tideFactor updated
- scripts/smoke-narration.ts            — TideState shape

